h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Mapeou instalação completa de SQL Server para Windows 11</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Mapeou instalação completa de SQL Server para Windows 11</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Perfeito. Vamos do zero. O roteiro completo é:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Etapa 1 → Instalar SQL Server Developer</strong> (gratuito, funcionalidades completas)
<strong>Etapa 2 → Instalar SSMS</strong> (interface gráfica)
<strong>Etapa 3 → Criar o repositório GitHub</strong>
<strong>Etapa 4 → Gerar e rodar os scripts</strong></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Etapa 1 — SQL Server Developer Edition</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Acessa esse link e baixa: <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://www.microsoft.com/pt-br/sql-server/sql-server-downloads">https://www.microsoft.com/pt-br/sql-server/sql-server-downloads</a></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Rola a página até a seção "Edições gratuitas especializadas" e clica em <strong>Baixar agora</strong> embaixo de <strong>Developer</strong>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Vai baixar um instalador pequeno (~5MB). Ao abrir:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Escolhe <strong>Básico</strong> (Basic) — instala tudo que precisamos sem configuração manual</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Aceita a licença e escolhe o diretório de instalação (o padrão já serve)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Aguarda a instalação terminar (uns 5–10 minutos)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">No final aparece uma tela de conclusão com a <strong>connection string</strong> — anota ou deixa aberta, mas o SSMS vai encontrar o servidor automaticamente.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Etapa 2 — SSMS</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Na mesma tela de conclusão do instalador do SQL Server tem um botão <strong>Instalar SSMS</strong>. Clica nele — vai abrir o site da Microsoft. Baixa e instala normalmente (next, next, finish).</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Se já fechou a tela, acessa direto: <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://aka.ms/ssmsfullsetup">https://aka.ms/ssmsfullsetup</a></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Me avisa quando os dois estiverem instalados e abertos que a gente parte pra criar o banco e os scripts.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
